{"data":{"actions":[{"callId":"chatcmpl-tool-88308322fe097101","input":{"filename":"migration_planner_report.md","title":"Prioritized Action Report – Migration Planner","markdown":"# Prioritized Action Report – Migration Planner (2026‑06‑18)\n\n**Evidence Used**\n- Dossier loaded (agent ID: 14‑migration‑planner). \n- Records analyzed (3 items, total risk 20, opportunity 9.8). See `analyze_records` output.\n\n## 1. High‑Priority Action (Urgent)\n| Record ID | Title | Impact | Risk Score | Opportunity Score | Recommended Action |\n|----------|-------|--------|------------|-------------------|-------------------|\n| 14‑A | Migration planner priority case | 46,438 | 10 (high) | 6.6 | **Proceed with execution plan** – allocate dedicated engineering resources, define rollback steps, and schedule a sprint‑level implementation. Validate inventory completeness before start.\n\n**Rationale**: Highest impact and risk score, already marked *urgent*. The agent’s core mission aligns directly with this record, making it the fastest win.\n\n## 2. Medium‑Priority Action (Blocked – Needs Coordination)\n| Record ID | Title | Impact | Risk Score | Opportunity Score | Recommended Action |\n|----------|-------|--------|------------|-------------------|-------------------|\n| 14‑C | Migration planner blocked follow‑up | 20,954 | 7 | 2.1 | **Unblock via cross‑functional meeting** – identify dependencies (e.g., legacy service owners, security reviews). Draft a lightweight RACI matrix and set a 2‑week deadline for resolution.\n\n**Rationale**: Substantial impact but currently blocked. Removing the blocker unlocks ~45% of total impact.\n\n## 3. Low‑Priority Action (In Review)\n| Record ID | Title | Impact | Risk Score | Opportunity Score | Recommended Action |\n|----------|-------|--------|------------|-------------------|-------------------|\n| 14‑B | Migration planner routine queue item | 10,582 | 3 | 1.1 | **Schedule for next planning cycle** – treat as a routine refinement. Can be bundled